{"tid":2369400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅冠聰料引致保皇黨震盪","createTime":"2021-01-17T06:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T07:05:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"32711bed9fb2cef549093f5286dff41ed6e89816","tid":2369400,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:10:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/CNMCM3ME7VGXVFBWFIQDOSDFAY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FCNMCM3ME7VGXVFBWFIQDOSDFAY%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=8d38850f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FCNMCM3ME7VGXVFBWFIQDOSDFAY%2F&h=eb02c982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/CNMCM3ME7VGXVFBWFIQDOSDFAY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰料引致保皇黨震盪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LuyZrsaXWKzqvhrhFZybW-LDYO4=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PHVUJONERVB3TIFIB7ZNKF5NQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLuyZrsaXWKzqvhrhFZybW-LDYO4%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPHVUJONERVB3TIFIB7ZNKF5NQ4.jpg&h=4b02db36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■羅冠聰預計美方新一輪制裁會令建制派陣腳大亂；圖為他去年8月在英國出席聲援港人集會。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國財政部最新制裁名單之中，全國人大常委譚耀宗及數名國安處人員成為「新貴」。流亡英國的前香港眾志主席羅冠聰認為，譚耀宗作為港版國安法推手之一，被制裁是意料之內，他相信是次制裁會「引來一片保皇黨內部的震盪」。有國際學者則相信，為中央政府與香港擔任「橋樑」的人士，將會陸續上榜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者：更多「橋樑」上榜<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰在社交網站回應最新一份制裁名單，認為譚耀宗作為全港唯一曾參與港版國安法立法的人，在早前民主派初選大搜捕期間，又聲稱初選目的明顯有違國安法，遭美國制裁是意料之內。而在建制陣營中屬重量級人士的譚耀宗被制裁，羅冠聰相信：「也會引來一片保皇黨內部的震盪。」並嘲諷提倡禁止雙重國籍、反制英國BNO「5+1」移民政策的新民黨主席葉劉淑儀：「一直覬覦登上國際頭版的葉劉淑儀也許正在慨嘆為何生不逢時，要加倍努力吸引制裁了。」<br />\n<br />\n香港教育大學亞洲及政策研究。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n關仲然估計，隨着中美關係日漸升溫。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d139cc41789b1e959c880265c3a1d6a05219fd99","tid":2369400,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/wong-08_FAyrZ_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwong-08_FAyrZ_1200x0.png&h=9831e144&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10fdd35f75ee40002ea2cc6b544638530c30a44e","tid":2369400,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:12:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c970e270d3a3e39e4461dd41a4bc75438e219b18","tid":2369400,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:20:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">有國際學者則相信，為中央政府與香港擔任「橋樑」的人士，將會陸續上榜。</span><br />\n<br />\n得番兩日，仲有冇可能「陸續上榜」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e793033a7a9ef8b60363347fed3f48b23127b6","tid":2369400,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:21:36.000Z","msg":"拜登唔會制裁啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169d5b6e264e8793b216f515a0ca881e536506e3","tid":2369400,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}